videos.description: Off an LSU miss, Ben Simmons flies in for the huge one-handed put back dunk to put a cap on LSU's upset of Kentucky.
videos.headline: Simmons' monster slam puts exclamation point on win

videos.description: Jay Bilas and Brad Nessler break down LSU's win that saw three different Tigers post double-doubles, showing that the team as a whole is starting to come together.
videos.headline: Team effort leads LSU over Kentucky
